A smart alarm clock with sleep phase tracking and a dozen useful features.&nbsp;

Price in the App Store: $20,94 / year

Only for iOS 10 or later.

A people’s sleep passes in various phases: from deep to fast. The Sleep Cycle app tracks your movements, detects the current phase with a microphone or accelerometer, and wakes you up at the right time.

Main functions:

sleep analysis, statistics and graphs of sleep, integration with the Health application;
tracking and measuring snoring;
customizable alarm period, work in the background;
export sleep data to Excel.

Premium Activated Features:

a large number of sounds and melodies for the alarm clock;
long-term sleep trends;
help for sleep (contributes to speedy falling asleep);
assessment of mood after sleep;
assessment of weather conditions for sleep, the ability to measure the pulse after sleep;
Philips HUE lamp support;
… and much more.

